付出&gt;收入先可以做落去,屌佢啦,點撚野可持續性?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有D教條主義又係麻撚煩<br />\n你坐一次地鐵又唔係黃,你去7-11買包煙又對唔住手足<br />\n我話俾你聽,有淘寶有安全軍火賣,淘黎香港唔會俾狗捉,我第一時間淘落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7d20e0ed362372ec2ce8bff6175155d01b4acb4","tid":1980161,"uid":39320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"068fae90b6a4ad9eed70bc6a52c801fd72fe1ec0","tid":1980161,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"ffd1442fd3e8abe1dcc1e0207909951070de1cc4","tid":1980161,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f530fb627141c67cbc838e61a849b1f3a575a06","tid":1980161,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:31:56.000Z","msg":"打交個比喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算多個人喺自己嗰邊就算齋企都好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:34:32.000Z","msg":"果D人會話某個某個係抽你後腳既隊友<br />\n但叫佢講實質抽後腳既例子,佢只會講D人血饅頭之類既說話"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:39:26.000Z","msg":"熱狗式嚟,你講東佢講西<br />\n詳情可參考高學歷廢青巴打啲post"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:47:58.000Z","msg":"無野搵野黎嗌 有破壞無建設"},{"pid":"74d40b343979873cd280643e23a0a190a0ba17aa","tid":1980161,"uid":282115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:49:41.000Z","msg":"杜生打大交個比喻幾好<br />\n之前都用過<br />\n<br />\n偽黃又好真黃又好<br />\n企得係我哋隔離<br />\n只要唔係背後桶刀就得啦"},{"pid":"47cb59f852d5dda558f6db9edbfd68c352c2bcad","tid":1980161,"uid":289115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f9601952f2c03c97dcd3eb943c5605ef98c364","tid":1980161,"uid":140218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T02:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0af9e9b0aa2f590b5109f37398a19964b23979","tid":1980161,"uid"